t: Efficient Network Printing with LPD for Error-Free Management | Lenovo USOutlet
s: LPD (line printer daemon) is a program that runs in the background of many operating systems supporting network printing. When you send a document to a printer in a network that uses LPD, the LPD queues your print job until the printer is ready.
